# Delphi cron — Hermes Agent cadences (standard crontab syntax).
# The demo does NOT use cron; it runs the whole sequence once via `make demo-delphi`.
# m h dom mon dow   command
*/5  * * * *   hermes run delphi/scanner
*/5  * * * *   hermes run delphi/arb-partition
*/15 * * * *   hermes run delphi/arb-crossvenue
*/10 * * * *   hermes run delphi/bot-doctor
0    9 * * *   hermes run delphi/brief --newly-listed
